I am very very excited to welcome you to the Apple website. As you know, I have a love-hate relationship with Apple computers. You probably guessed that when I started using this website, I was not a fan. Not because they don’t have a good product.

I am a fan because it’s a wonderful technology, especially if you love the Apple iOS.

That said, their products can be slow.

Wednesday, July 13, 2009

Apple Crisp!

We had an evening out in town recently and wanted to have some fun, so we brought out a few more apple cider in the case. My brother and I went out on our bikes and rode down to a place called Apple Pies. We arrived and had one large apple pie, with just an apple and a crust.
